{"id":232784372,"title":"沒有","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafbfa1/1280.jpeg\n一個圓圈那樣\n沒有頭尾\n汲汲營營也好偽裝逃避也好\n到頭來\n全不剩半點殘留\n。\n早晨的城市飄落雨滴\n前一晚被遺忘的安全帽裡於是\n積滿整個夜晚的潮濕\n還未燃盡就被彈落的煙頭在柏油的坑洞裡\n熄滅\n\n預將啟程的旅人於是提前到達終點\n從未出發\n於是景色依舊如常\n在被忘卻的夢境裡風光明媚\n一如想像\n。\n搭建的關聯是虛線\n在城市座落的島嶼的灰濛濛天上\n被雨水洗落\n殘留下\n沒有回覆的訊息\n殘留下\n各個被敷衍推卻的邀約\n\n沒有交集\n\n通透的雨衣阻隔冷風阻隔水滴\n卻從未能拉緊的縫隙裡滲透\n青灰色的焦躁濕黏髮稍\n被鑲嵌進假日壅塞的車流\n在狹小道路上動彈不得\n。","excerpt":"一個圓圈那樣，沒有頭尾，汲汲營營也好偽裝逃避也好，到頭來，全不剩半點殘留，。早晨的城市飄落雨滴，前一晚被遺忘的安全帽裡於是，積滿整個夜晚的潮濕，還未燃盡就被彈落的煙頭在柏油的坑洞裡，熄滅，預將啟程的旅","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-29T13:39:15.877Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-29T13:39:15.877Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["玖伍言"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"玖伍捌肆","department":"outsideman","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafbfa1/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"ac9f0f26-ef4d-44f8-916e-89f8ea212ac6","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafbfa1/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafbfa1/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafbfa1/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2019-12-29T13:39:15.877Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-29T13:39:15.877Z","width":640,"height":640},{"id":"ac9f0f26-ef4d-44f8-916e-89f8ea212ac6","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/755e9099-6c8b-4113-9837-d4c7eeafb